[2C[3A]0;⠂ Chat and storytelling session[2D[3B[4A  A lighthouse keeper named Odette lived alone on a rock that the sea had been trying to swallow for two[1B   hundred[1Cyears.[1CEvery[1Cnight[1Cshe[1Cclimbed[1Cthe[1Cspiral[1Cstairs,[1Clit[1Cthe[1Clamp,[1Cand[1Cwatched[1Cthe[1Cdark[1Cwater[1B  for ships that almost never came.                                                                     [2C[1B                
