[2C[3A]0;⠐ Chat and storytelling session]0;⠂ Chat and storytelling session[2D[3B[4A  One winter, a bottle washed up on the shore. Inside was a letter, in handwriting she didn't recognize,[1B   that[1Cread:[1C[3mThank you for the light last Tuesday. I would not have made it home.[1C[23mNo[1Csignature.[1CNo[1B  ship's name.                                                                                          [2C[1B                
