[2C[3A[2D[3B[2K[G[1A[6A[38;5;231m⏺[1C[39mThere was a clockmaker in a small[1Cmountain[1Ctown[1Cwho[1Cbuilt[1Ca[1Cclock[1Cwith[1Cthirteen[1Chours.[1B                                                                                            [1B[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[1B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m                                                                                                     [1B[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[1B[39m  [38;5;246mesc to interrupt[39m                                                                                      [1B                                                                                                        [2C[3A]0;⠂ Chat and storytelling session]0;⠐ Chat and storytelling session]0;⠂ Chat and storytelling session[2D[3B[4A  He hid the thirteenth hour between eleven and midnight, in a notch of brass no bigger than a          [1B  fingernail.[1CNobody[1Cnoticed.[1CThe[1Cclock[1Ckept[1Ctime[1Clike[1Cany[1Cother[1C—[1Cchimed[1Cat[1Cnoon,[1Cchimed[1Cat[1Csix,[1Cthe[1B  baker still opened at five — but once a day, for sixty unaccounted minutes, the town slipped sideways [2C[1Binto a quiet that[1Cnobody[1Cremembered[1Cafterward.

