[2C[3A]0;⠐ Chat and storytelling session]0;⠂ Chat and storytelling session[2D[3B[4A  In that hour, the clockmaker did the things he could not do in the other twelve. He wrote letters to  [1B  his[1Cdead[1Cwife.[1CHe[1Cleft[1Cbread[1Con[1Cthe[1Cdoorstep[1Cof[1Cthe[1Cwidow[1Ctwo[1Cstreets[1Cover,[1Cwho[1Cnever[1Cfigured[1Cout[1B  where it came from. He sat on the church steps and cried without anyone seeing.                       [2C[1B                
